description:
This is an alpha version of PowerMiner. This is buggy right now, so you may as well wait for the next alpha version. Right now this game has following features:

 - Infinite terrain*
 - Random world generator
 - 9 different blocks
 - Backwards compatibility with Movement Batch maps

*The maximum limit in blocks of the world is the maximum of 32-bit integer

This is actually the first version of PowerMiner that is publically available, so you can download it here: https://bit.ly/3WskiWu
The project has been renamed due its use in other batch file by other person.
